Welcome to SilverStack Nexus Repository Manager Lab! 📦

Nexus is running internally at http://localhost:__NEXUS_PORT__
Nginx reverse proxy is listening on port 80 (internal)

Tools:

- cloudflared         Cloudflare Tunnel for public access
- java 21             Modern LTS Java runtime
- arkade  jq  yq  fx  task  just  fzf  btop  cfssl  ripgrep

Default Nexus credentials:
  Username: admin
  Password: cat /opt/sonatype-work/nexus3/admin.password  (first login only)

To expose Nexus publicly via Cloudflare Tunnel:

  1. Go to dash.cloudflare.com/one → Networks → Connectors
  2. Create tunnel → choose Cloudflared → name it (e.g. nexus-lab) → save
  3. Copy & run the install command shown:  sudo cloudflared service install <token>
  4. Add a published application route:
       Subdomain: nexus   Domain: yourdomain.com
       Service:   HTTP    URL:    localhost:80
  5. Nexus is now live at https://nexus.yourdomain.com

Quick commands:
  nexus-status  nexus-logs  nexus-restart  nexus-start  nexus-stop
  nginx-status  nginx-logs  nginx-reload

